snippet.title: Official Tower of Saviors Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Tower of Saviors by Mad Head Limited

The new version 2.0 comes with a whole new series of battling strategies, we're kicking it up a notch for summoners!

★ 30 New monsters
★ 13 New skills
★ Descent of New Bosses
★ New battle scene
★ New player-to-player chat system
★ Optimized interface usage and visual enhancements

ITunes Store Page:

https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/tower-of-saviors/id584713830

Homepage:

http://www.towerofsaviors.com/en.html
